text: Renée Jeanne Hugon (21 September 1930 - 7 July 2015) was a French gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2015 deaths Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Paris
